v id="i19"><div id="about-photo"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhQABAAIAAAMXFxQAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAABAAEAAAAJFhI+py+0Po5y02ouz3rz7D4biSJbmiabqyrbuC8fyTNf2jef6zvf+DwwKh8Si8YhMKpfMpvMJjUqn1Kr1is1qt9yuF1AAADs=" lazyload="images/steven-ciacco-pfc-performance-fitness-centers.jpg" style="width: 100%; height: auto;" width="0" height="0"></div><div class="about-text"><div><span style="background-color: inherit;">Steven Ciaccio, former professional mixed martial arts fighter and champion, started Performance Fitness Centers in 2015. Since then he has been helping clients reach their fitness goals in a positive, encouraging, and safe environment.</span><br></div><div></div></div><div style="clear: both;"></div></div><div id="i22"></div><div id="i23"><div><span style="background-color: inherit;">All of our training programs are designed by a professional exercise scientist in consultation with an experienced exercise psychologist, resulting in enjoyable training experiences that lead to sustained results, without injuries. </span></div><div><span style="background-color: inherit;"><br></span></div><div><span style="background-color: inherit;">Our process begins with a face-to-face meeting, where we sit down and listen to you tell us what you want to accomplish. We then design a custom program for you, based on your personality, starting point, and individual needs. We then train with you every step of the way as you make progress toward reaching your fitness goals.</span><br></div><div><br></div><div>If you’ve tried all the rest and are still unsatisfied, give us a call today. We would love to meet you and help you get the fitness results you’ve always wanted.</div><div><br></div><span style="background-color: inherit;">Call us today! The initial consultation does not cost you anything, so you have nothing to lose and everything to gain. <a href="contact.php"><u>Call us now</u></a>!</span> </div></div><div id="i24"><div id="i25">Questions? Call us: 909-293-8814</div></d